platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Oddmar is overflowing with imaginative visual designs and creative challenges. One moment you might be gawking at beautifully rendered water, then grip your device white-knuckled as youre whisked into an alternate realm of fast-moving spiked walls. With stunning artistry, humor, and a constant supply of surprises, Oddmar is a enchanting platformer. It introduces new ideas at just the right pace to maintain an exciting blend of the familiar and unexpected.
